{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/block-proc-lambda-in-ruby/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Liang's Blog"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"29058a65-e24a-5118-bb01-12a44e30deaa","excerpt":"Block block 其实就是一些可以被执行的代码段，block 的语法有 2 中形式，一种是 do…end 形式，一种是简写的{}形式，例如： block 一般跟 times 或者 each，collect 等方法一起使用，可以对某一个 hash 或者 array 中的元素进行操作。\n用 yield…","html":"<h4>Block</h4>\n<p>block 其实就是一些可以被执行的代码段，block 的语法有 2 中形式，一种是 do…end 形式，一种是简写的{}形式，例如：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"ruby\"><pre class=\"language-ruby\"><code class=\"language-ruby\">array1 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\narray1<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token keyword\">each</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">do</span> <span class=\"token operator\">|</span>n<span class=\"token operator\">|</span>\n    puts n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">end</span>\narray1<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token keyword\">each</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token operator\">|</span>n<span class=\"token operator\">|</span> puts n <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>block 一般跟 times 或者 each，collect 等方法一起使用，可以对某一个 hash 或者 array 中的元素进行操作。\n用 yield 方法可以让函数接受一个 block，例如：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"ruby\"><pre class=\"language-ruby\"><code class=\"language-ruby\"><span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token method-definition\"><span class=\"token function\">block_test</span></span>\n  puts <span class=\"token string\">\"we are in the method!\"</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">yield</span>\n  puts <span class=\"token string\">\"we are back in the method!\"</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">end</span>\nblock_test <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> puts <span class=\"token string\">\"we are in the block!\"</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>这样当函数执行到 yield 语句时候，就会调用传入的 block。同时 yield 还可以处理传入的参数</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"ruby\"><pre class=\"language-ruby\"><code class=\"language-ruby\"><span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token method-definition\"><span class=\"token function\">block_test</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>name<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  puts <span class=\"token string\">\"we are in the method!\"</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">yield</span> name\n  puts <span class=\"token string\">\"we are back in the method!\"</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">end</span>\nblock_test<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"block\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token operator\">|</span>name<span class=\"token operator\">|</span> puts <span class=\"token string\">\"we are in the <span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token delimiter tag\">#{</span>name<span class=\"token delimiter tag\">}</span></span>!\"</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h4>proc</h4>\n<p>在 ruby 中“任何都是对象”，但是其实对于 blok 来讲，它并不是对象，这是 ruby 中的一个例外，block 不能保存到变量中，没有一个真正的对象使用起来那么方便，因此我们需要…proc, 它可以看做是保存成变量的 block，这样我们可以给这个 block 起个名字，并可以重复调用它。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"ruby\"><pre class=\"language-ruby\"><code class=\"language-ruby\">multiply_of_3 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">Proc</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">do</span> <span class=\"token operator\">|</span>n<span class=\"token operator\">|</span>\n  n<span class=\"token operator\">%</span><span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token operator\">==</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">end</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">1.</span><span class=\"token number\">.100</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>select<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">&amp;</span>multiply_of_3<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>为什么要用 proc 呢，这里有 2 点需要理解的</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Procs 是一个完全的对象，它具有所有对象的属性。</li>\n<li>Procs 在创建之后，可以在其他地方被重复调用，而 block 显然是不行的。</li>\n</ol>\n<p>我们可以直接使用 Ruby 的<code>.call</code>方法来调用一个 Proc</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"ruby\"><pre class=\"language-ruby\"><code class=\"language-ruby\">test <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">Proc</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\ntest<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>call</code></pre></div>\n<h4>Lambda</h4>\n<p>与 proc 一样，lambda 也是对象，从一些语法和行为上来看，lambda 跟 proc 在很多地方都是相同的。让我们来看一个 lambda 的例子吧</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"ruby\"><pre class=\"language-ruby\"><code class=\"language-ruby\">lambda <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> puts <span class=\"token string\">\"hello\"</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>与下面这个 proc 是相同的</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"ruby\"><pre class=\"language-ruby\"><code class=\"language-ruby\"><span class=\"token builtin\">Proc</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> puts <span class=\"token string\">\"hello\"</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>我们可以把一个 lambda 作为一个参数传递给一个函数</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"ruby\"><pre class=\"language-ruby\"><code class=\"language-ruby\"><span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token method-definition\"><span class=\"token function\">test_lambda</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>p_lambda<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  puts <span class=\"token string\">\"I am the lambda test method.\"</span>\n  p_lambda<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>call\n<span class=\"token keyword\">end</span>\ntest_lambda<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>lambda <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> puts <span class=\"token string\">\"I am the real lambda!\"</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>从以上例子可以看出来，可以通过以下方式来定义一个 lambda\n<code class=\"language-text\">lambda { block }</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"ruby\"><pre class=\"language-ruby\"><code class=\"language-ruby\">strings <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Germany\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Netherland\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token string\">\"England\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token string\">\"France\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\nsymbolize <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> lambda <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token operator\">|</span>n<span class=\"token operator\">|</span> n<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>to_sym <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\nsymbol <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> strings<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>collect<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">&amp;</span>symbolize<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>lambda 和 proc 的不同点：<br>\nlambda 会检查传入的参数数量，如果你传入了错误的参数数量，lambda 会抛出一个异常，而 proc 不会检查，但是只会置为 nil。<br>\nlambda 在返回后会把控制权交给调用函数，而 proc 在返回后不会把控制权交给调用函数。</p>\n<p>下面这个 proc 可以执行一下看下输出：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"ruby\"><pre class=\"language-ruby\"><code class=\"language-ruby\"><span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token method-definition\"><span class=\"token function\">batman_ironman_proc</span></span>\n  victor <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">Proc</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Batman will win!\"</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  victor<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>call\n  <span class=\"token string\">\"Iron man will win!\"</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">end</span>\nputs batman_ironman_proc</code></pre></div>\n<p>我们可以看到结果，在 Proc 调用之后就结束了</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"ruby\"><pre class=\"language-ruby\"><code class=\"language-ruby\"><span class=\"token constant\">Batman</span> will win<span class=\"token operator\">!</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>再来看一个 lambda 的例子</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"ruby\"><pre class=\"language-ruby\"><code class=\"language-ruby\"><span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token method-definition\"><span class=\"token function\">batman_ironman_lambda</span></span>\n  victor <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> lambda <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Batman will win!\"</span>\n  victor<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>call\n  <span class=\"token string\">\"Iron man will win!\"</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">end</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>我们可以看到结果，在 lambda 调用之后回到了原来的函数中</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"ruby\"><pre class=\"language-ruby\"><code class=\"language-ruby\"><span class=\"token constant\">Iron</span> man will win<span class=\"token operator\">!</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>block,proc,lambda 入门学习就先到这里，希望以后可以深入研究。</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Block, proc, lambda in Ruby","date":"October 27, 2013","description":"ruby learning notes"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/block-proc-lambda-in-ruby/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/pomodoro-technique/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Pomodoro time technique"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/strong-parameters-in-rails4/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Strong parameters in rails4"}}}}}